<h1>Created new Chat Room!</h1>
<p class="error-text">Careful! The following Room ID and Password is required to login to the Chatroom. This Information is not stored anywhere, please safe it somewhere.</p>
<div class="newRoom-container">
    <ul>
        <li>Room ID: <%= roomID %></li>
        <li>Password: <%= password %></li>
